snippet.title: Total War Battles: WARHAMMER First Announcement Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Officially licensed by Creative Assembly and Games Workshop, to be developed and published by NetEase Games, the mass-battled mobile game based on the epic of Warhammer Fantasy --Total War Battles: WARHAMMER will be brought to your fingertips!

Official Website: https://www.totalwarbattles.com/warhammer/
Discord: https://discord.gg/nUJXB8pss5
